title: Happy Hour #58: I Woke Up Like This
itunes:title: Happy Hour #58: I Woke Up Like This
description:
Anney and Samantha wind down the week with some drinks while chatting about the pressure for women to be graceful both in sleeping and waking up, and the vulnerability of letting someone see you in all of your states. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
